OL,3,C'They get forgotten': Funeral home
OL,4,Creuniting families with unclaimed ashes
OL,6,FA Nottingham funeral parlour says it's
OL,7,Fpart of a national mission to reunited
OL,8,Fhundreds of thousands of unclaimed
OL,9,Furns with their families.
OL,11,FA.W. Lymn's shelves are lined with the
OL,12,Ffinal remains of 136 people.
OL,14,FThe parlour has uploaded the details
OL,15,Fof every urn they hold since 2000.
OL,17,FThey are the first funeral home in the
OL,18,FUK to use the 'The Ash Register'. The
OL,19,Fwebsite uses a map display to show
OL,20,Funclaimed remains across the UK.
