OL,3,C'They get forgotten': Funeral home
OL,4,Creuniting families with unclaimed ashes
OL,6,FSitting in A.W. Lymn's storage room
OL,7,Fare the ashes of George Maxwell Lawson
OL,8,FCBE.
OL,10,FMr Lawson first enlisted in the Royal
OL,11,FLeicestershire Regiment in 1915 and
OL,12,Fserved for thirty years.
OL,14,FHe was decorated for conspicuous
OL,15,Fgallantry and devotion to duty in the
OL,16,FFirst World War and he helped lead
OL,17,FBritain's air defence in the Second
OL,18,FWorld War.
OL,20,FHis remains have been there for over
OL,21,Fsix decades.
