OL,3,C'They get forgotten': Funeral home
OL,4,Creuniting families with unclaimed ashes
OL,6,FMr Lymn Rose said:
OL,8,F"As a fifth-generation family business
OL,9,Fthat has been supporting the bereaved
OL,10,Fin the region for nearing 120 years,
OL,11,Fwe feel a deep sense of responsibility
OL,12,Fand duty of care to look after
OL,13,Fcremated remains in our possession, in
OL,14,Fthe hope that they will one day find
OL,15,Ftheir way back to someone."
OL,17,FRichard Martin, the founder of the
OL,18,FArchive, said:
