OL,3,C'They get forgotten': Funeral home
OL,4,Creuniting families with unclaimed ashes
OL,6,F"Our goal is simple and it's to
OL,7,Freunite as many people as possible
OL,8,Fwith the ashes of a relative or loved
OL,9,Fone. We feel so passionate about
OL,10,Fhistory not being lost in time, which
OL,11,Fis why we set up this website to
OL,12,Fprovide a space for people to document
OL,13,Fsomeone's final resting place."
